\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection

\series bold
Compare low- vs high-skilled
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Using the stored stationary panel (you may pool all 200 periods),
 compare outcomes for low- and high-skilled workers.
 Report and discuss at least:
 the unemployment rate by type,
 the mean and standard deviation of 
\begin_inset Formula $\log y$
\end_inset

